In the other sectors of the processing industry, the rate of increase in prices varies from 0.6% to 9.1%.
In total in the manufacturing industry last year prices rose by 10.2%.
The prices in the electricity, gas, steam and water supply sector exceeded 18.7% last year's prices.
In domestic sales among target groups of sectors, the highest monthly price increase occurred in August in sectors producing investment goods (0.7%).
